{
  "texts": [
    "A major challenge is how to decide when to exit early, a non-trivial problem for the object detection task.",
    "We explain our approach to designing an early-exit decision-making module in Sect. 5.3.",
    "Training our dynamic DNN with the network pruning and early exit functionality involves a multi-step process, as it should train multiple exit branches.",
    "We build our training process on top of existing multi-step training strategies adopted in the early exit paradigm (Laskaridis et al. 2021; Matsubara et al. 2023).",
    "Our multi-step training process works as follows: In the first step, the main exit branch is trained end-to-end together with the backbone DNN."
  ]
}